Grand Prix awarded to Matteo Garrone for Reality
2012-05-28 02:45:47 GMT
The Grand Prix was awarded to Matteo Garrone for his film Reality.After receiving the prize, awarded to him by Leila Hatami, the winner said: "Thank you to the Festival, thank you to the actors, thank you to the production. Ciao!"
